# Test and benchmark code for `libdpu`

## Compilation

- Copy upmem's `backends` source into the subfolder `upmem-libdpu`
  Either by downloading http://sdk-releases.upmem.com/2023.2.0/upmem-src-2023.2.0-Linux-x86_64.tar.gz (and extracting ONLY src/backends)
  or by cloning https://github.com/manpen/upmem-libdpu

- Run make

## Own compilation
```
mkdir build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -GNinja ..
ln -sf /usr/share/ upmem-libdpu/share
ln -sf /home/manpen/code/upmem-communication/build/upmem-libdpu/hw/libdpuhw.so upmem-libdpu/api/
```